_:N5f1499d7dfdd4a8693c1bd1966bc9538 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Wes Streeting was Secretary of State for Health and Social Care from 5 July 2024 to 14 May 2026. He was elected as the MP for Ilford North in July 2024.</p>\n" .
